&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;Audio transcript&lt;/summary&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;As you sketch your vision, consider how your career focused services might fit into an overall ELA program that also includes a focus on civics and/or family literacy. The article “From Surviving to Thriving” can offer some ideas to get you thinking.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you like to consider the big picture, consider watching Effective Collaboration in Multi-disciplinary teams. It explains how divergent thinking can result in better ideas and describes the power of collective impact. The video is a bit long but you might find it worthwhile. Feel free to just dip into it and watch as much as is useful to you.&lt;/p&gt;
