        <title>Post Self-Assessment</title>
        <contents>&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Listen to audio:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="@@PLUGINFILE@@/ELL_Mod3_2230.mp3"&gt;ELL_Mod3_2230.mp3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;Audio transcript&lt;/summary&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt; You most likely have gained a great deal of information by completing this unit, not all of which you may be able to remember. Here is your chance to see where you feel confident in your ability to explain and describe key elements of career focused contextualization. If you feel weak in a particular area, feel free to reread particular sections and please share your new knowledge and insights with your colleagues and partners&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/details&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium; line-height: 1.231;"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium; line-height: 1.231;"&gt;Now that you might know a bit more, here is your chance to self-assess what you can do with that knowledge.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr" style="margin-left: 30px;"&gt;&lt;b style="font-size: medium; line-height: 1.231;"&gt;&lt;span id="docs-internal-guid-0f054c75-7665-902b-ef92-e97d40c39e6c"&gt;Statement 1: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span id="docs-internal-guid-0f054c75-7665-902b-ef92-e97d40c39e6c" style="font-size: medium; line-height: 1.231;"&gt;I can discuss how the new directions in Adult Education will shape our program services for ELLs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-left: 30px;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span id="docs-internal-guid-0f054c75-7665-b45c-8221-df91f6da1af4"&gt;Statement 2: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span id="docs-internal-guid-0f054c75-7665-b45c-8221-df91f6da1af4"&gt;I can list the workforce preparation activities that WIOA highlights&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id="docs-internal-guid-0f054c75-7665-b45c-8221-df91f6da1af4"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-left: 30px;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span id="docs-internal-guid-0f054c75-7665-d42b-10ad-b4574f4bf854"&gt;Statement 3: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span id="docs-internal-guid-0f054c75-7665-d42b-10ad-b4574f4bf854"&gt;I can explain the key elements of a comprehensive ELA contextualization program&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-left: 30px;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span id="docs-internal-guid-0f054c75-7666-0731-a62e-ca3cf67b7f11"&gt;Statement 4: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span id="docs-internal-guid-0f054c75-7666-0731-a62e-ca3cf67b7f11"&gt;I can describe the different models used to prepare ELLs and others for career pathways&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
